Subject: [Rd] Why does poly work for unordered factors?
In-Reply-To: <64bc8b21-67c9-4ce4-bb4a-3c9bbe0d5397@thuenen.de>
References: <1a60d37e-454d-4452-854b-cfb9036d3e46@thuenen.de>
